erage</p></div><div class="maturity-card current "><div class="maturity-card-header"><span class="maturity-card-level">Level 2</span><span class="current-badge">Current</span></div><h4 class="maturity-card-title">Growing</h4><p class="maturity-card-description">Some coverage</p></div><div class="maturity-card  "><div class="maturity-card-header"><span class="maturity-card-level">Level 3</span></div><h4 class="maturity-card-title">Solid</h4><p class="maturity-card-description">Good coverage</p></div><div class="maturity-card  "><div class="maturity-card-header"><span class="maturity-card-level">Level 4</span></div><h4 class="maturity-card-title">Comprehensive</h4><p class="maturity-card-description">Full coverage</p></div></div><div class="justification-section"><h4 class="justification-header">Justification</h4><div class="justification-text"><p>Still catching up</p></div></div></div></div></section>"`;

